 cm←{names}CorrelMatrix x;avex;delt;sosq;srsos;sxy;cros;names;mdelt;⎕ML;⎕IO

     ⍝∇ the correlation matrix between the input vector of vectors

 ⎕ML←⎕IO←1
 :If 1=≡x ⋄ x←↓[1]x ⋄ :EndIf
 avex←Dutils.Average¨x
 delt←x-avex
 sosq←Dutils.SumByTwos¨delt×delt
 srsos←sosq*0.5
 mdelt←↓↑delt
 sxy←Dutils.SumByTwos¨mdelt∘.×mdelt
 cros←srsos∘.×srsos

 cm←3 Dutils.RndDP¨sxy÷cros
 :If 0=⎕NC'names'
     names←'X',∘⍕¨⍳≢cm
 :EndIf
 cm←(' ',names),names⍪cm

 :Return
